About the game: â€‹ UFO Simulator Control Master is a physics based arcade/simulation game. The goal of this game is to abduct rescue missing astronauts by controlling a UFO in space. Get through the narrow passes, dodge the various traps with delicate control. And evacuate astronauts to the goal Area 51? within the time limit. Features You can explore the mystery and danger of space. There are two main play modes, including Arcade stages (2.5D style) and Simulation stages (3D style). The game uses a check point system so you will not lose your progress. Realistic UFO flight physics. Now you can enjoy the game in English, French, and Korean. This is Steam Greenlight (Greenlit) game. Thanks for all the supports!
